Class PrefixManagerWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unibz.krdb.obda.io.AbstractPrefixManager
      • it.unibz.krdb.obda.protege4.core.PrefixManagerWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrefixManager

    public class PrefixManagerWrapper
extends AbstractPrefixManager
    This PrefixManager is meant to 'wrap' Protege's prefix manager. That way any prefix defined in Protege are transparently passed to all OBDA lib classes.
